<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 md:flex-row flex-col items-center">
            <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pr-24 md:pr-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left mb-16 md:mb-0 items-center text-center">
                <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Our Mission</h1>
                <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">PHI's mission is to advance peace, stability, and human development across Africa by empowering communities affected by conflict, poverty, and social fragmentation. We believe that peace and progress are inseparable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-1/2 w-5/6">
                <img class="object-cover object-center rounded" alt="mission" src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2012/04/25/00/03/dove-41260_1280.png">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
        <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
                <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">PHI'S MISSION</h2>
                <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Building Peace, Empowering Communities</h1>
                <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">PHI focuses on three main pillars: Peacebuilding and Conflict Resolution, Humanitarian Relief and Recovery, and Social and Economic Development. Through partnerships and community-driven projects, PHI addresses root causes of instability and promotes long-term resilience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap">
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Peacebuilding and Conflict Resolution</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Promoting dialogue, reconciliation, and community cohesion through local peace committees, leadership training, and cultural understanding initiatives.</p>
                    <a class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Humanitarian Relief and Recovery</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Delivering targeted assistance to vulnerable groups, including food security, shelter, education, and psychosocial support for displaced or disadvantaged populations.</p>
                    <a class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Social and Economic Development</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Supporting long-term resilience through education programs, youth empowerment, vocational training, and sustainable livelihoods projects.</p>
                    <a class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
                    <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Community Partnerships</h2>
                    <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">PHI partners with local authorities, regional bodies, and international organizations to implement community-driven projects.</p>
                    <a class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center">Learn More
                        <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
